{"tid":1723322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［輿論戰］致仍然有使用 Facebook 的你","createTime":"2019-11-15T07:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T11:02:47.000Z","uid":124017,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"140ceddcc9e6285517436b2376f66629beddc941","tid":1723322,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"由於近日 Facebook 出現大量網軍抹黑示威者，亦有五毛軍表示，示威者不代表所有香港人的言論。<br />\n<br />\n如果仍然有用 Facebook 嘅你，請唔好吝嗇你嘅讚好功能。<br />\n<br />\n基本：例如睇新聞嘅時候，不妨比個讚或嬲嬲，留個言。<br />\n<br />\n進階：睇到有假帳號都用檢舉系統，雖然無咩用，但都檢舉咗先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深黃媒體已經會有手足招呼五毛，其他嘅新聞媒體，需要大家長期支援。<br />\n<br />\n香港：<br />\n雅虎新聞<br />\n香港01 (重災區）<br />\n有線新聞<br />\nnow新聞<br />\n<br />\n台灣：<br />\n東森新聞<br />\n三立新聞<br />\n<br />\n如有其他重要新聞媒體，請手足留言補充 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n人人有責 請各位多出一分綿力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfbaf3e722c5676c2995c15df08032daeeb0519","tid":1723322,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"自推 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb9ce9c9b43992feca9cc778f1902326afedf90","tid":1723322,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"自推 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871d6c48613e48f7a360e32397885ad42a01a0a1","tid":1723322,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e2693b172ba716b999bd9609039d04a492f4d87","tid":1723322,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"YouTube 三立果邊真係好多支那人留言<br />\n關於香港又留 關於台灣又留<br />\n屌 好煩"},{"pid":"5ef9de1443f2755e01e04f222d3dc47d83eddacc","tid":1723322,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:10:16.0